# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# FlowState — Environment Variables (VPS Production)
# Copy file này thành .env và điền đầy đủ
# KHÔNG commit file .env lên Git!
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── APP ──────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL="https://YOURDOMAIN.COM"
NEXTAUTH_URL="https://YOURDOMAIN.COM"

# Tạo bằng lệnh: openssl rand -base64 32
NEXTAUTH_SECRET="REPLACE_WITH_STRONG_RANDOM_SECRET"

# ─── DATABASE (PostgreSQL trên VPS) ───────────────────
POSTGRES_DB="flowstate"
POSTGRES_USER="flowstate"
# Tạo bằng lệnh: openssl rand -base64 24
POSTGRES_PASSWORD="REPLACE_WITH_STRONG_DB_PASSWORD"

# URL cho Next.js app (dùng tên service Docker)
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://flowstate:REPLACE_WITH_STRONG_DB_PASSWORD@postgres:5432/flowstate"

# ─── REDIS ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tạo bằng lệnh: openssl rand -base64 24
REDIS_PASSWORD="REPLACE_WITH_STRONG_REDIS_PASSWORD"
REDIS_URL="redis://:REPLACE_WITH_STRONG_REDIS_PASSWORD@redis:6379"

# ─── GOOGLE OAUTH ─────────────────────────────────────
# Lấy từ: console.cloud.google.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID="your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com"
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET="your-client-secret"

# ─── ADMIN ────────────────────────────────────────────
ADMIN_EMAIL="your-email@gmail.com"

# ─── OPTIONAL: Email (Resend.com - miễn phí 3000 email/tháng) ──
# RESEND_API_KEY="re_xxxxxxxxxxxx"
# EMAIL_FROM="noreply@YOURDOMAIN.COM"
